    <body> We worked on fixing some of the links that we realized were broken on the website (before some of our links were simply redirecting to the home page of the travel service, not exactly the desired result ...). We also created a logo, integrated it with our website, and worked on some of the aesthetic aspects of our site. We put the total elapsed time and total cost in bold lettering at the bottom of each route. Our logo is shown below.<br>
