    <h2>May 10, 2013</h2>
    <body> We presented our project demo today.  We met earlier in the day to debug our site a little more and practice our presentation. We found a bug in the New Jersey Transit scraping code, that was introduced the night before during a late night coding session. The bug was very subtle. Once we found it and fixed it, we ran through our demo before heading down to the presentation room. Our presentation seemed to go pretty smoothly.  
